snippet.textDisplay:
I never could tell you that I have loved you for 3 years. I am scared. Even as a friend, you are too precious to lose. I can't take that risk. I rather love you like this. Just you exist, that makes me the happiest. It's just I feel peace, calmness  when you are around. I can't loose you. One day I will tell you everything when you knowing or not knowing won't matter anymore. I don't wanna loose you. 

And you know, as I always said, When you wear blue saree, I can't take my eyes off from you. Everytime you are around me, I can't take my mind off from you. I miss our silence. 

You are the vortex, where even time dosen't exist. Once something is in, it will be there forever. Well, let me know you, I am in. The timeless place where I will stay forever. Even just your essence of existing there is worth to sacrifice my time. I will be happy.
